title: BAYC Purchase #2 & #3 (2/3) for MutantCats DAO
body: The top 2 voted BAYC's between the choices below will be purchased when the snapshot vote is complete. If any is bought out or delisted, we will purchase the next-in-ranking on the votes. Please go to OpenSea to see them, then come back here and vote accordingly. These BAYC's are picked with a tolerance of approximately 1-4ETH from the floor price.
